article.description: Devon Goodman had 21 points as Penn topped Brown 92-82 on Friday night. Bryce Washington added 20 points for the Quakers.
article.headline: Goodman carries Penn past Brown 92-82
article.story: PROVIDENCE, R.I. -- Devon Goodman had 21 points as Penn topped Brown 92-82 on Friday night. Bryce Washington added 20 points for the Quakers. AJ Brodeur had 18 points for Penn (14-7, 2/3 Ivy League). Michael Wang added 11 points. Obi Okolie scored a career-high 25 points for the Bears (13-8, 1-4). Desmond Cambridge added 21 points. Tamenang Choh had 11 points. Penn takes on Yale on the road on Saturday. Brown plays Princeton at home on Saturday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
